The unofficial app for finding and tracking Netflix, HBO, Apple+, Hulu, Amazon: Prime, and more originals and their release dates, quickly and easily.

With so many streaming providers, it's hard to find and keep track of great original shows and movies. But now with Rivr you can merge all the information from all your streaming services into one place or 'river', keep track of your favorites and discover new ones, and never miss an episode.

Quickly find all scheduled originals release dates, then get notified about changes and updates to the show or movie, including notifications about your favourite actors.

Keep track of what you watch by marking episodes and movies as watched, then rate them.

Set reminders for your favorite series release dates and get real-time notifications on changes, release dates and new trailers.

- Discover new content by streaming provider or genre;
-  Smart Subscriptions - Save on streaming services;
- Filter by Series, Movies or Documentaries;
- Mark episodes and movies as watched;
- Rate episodes and movies;
- Customised profile and recommendations;
- Season and episode rating charts;
- Compare ratings;
- Tabbed interface for easy navigating;
- Notification when the show is released;
- List of favorite shows, movies;
- Browse and Search for Original Shows/Movies;
- Browse by popular, rating, date, show, or movie;
- Watch Trailers;
- Currently works with Netflix, HBO, Apple+, Hulu, and Amazon: Prime. More are coming soon.

Rivr is funded by ads, if you choose to purchase Rivr Pro to hide these ads, unlock Smart Subscriptions, Premium notifications, and unlimited favorites and follows, payment will be charged to your iTunes account, and your account will be charged for renewal 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the iTunes Store after purchase. The current price for Rivr Pro is $0.99 USD per Month or $7.99 USD per Year and may vary from country to country.
Purchasing Rivr Pro will not allow you to stream or watch any content, shows, or movies.
