The APP controls the flight of the quadcopter through wireless WIFI image transmission technology.
It has the following functions:
1. Connect WIFI to control the flight of the aircraft through the joystick;
2. Display the real-time streaming picture of the aircraft camera;
3, take photos, video, view photos and videos;
4. Control the flight of the aircraft through gravity induction;
5. Automatic trajectory flight;
6. Voice-controlled flight;
7. Gesture recognition, taking photos and video;
8. VR mode;
9. Music video mode;
10. Video special effects mode.
